Title: Wrong Roads
Writer: Graham Yost (developed for television by), Dave Andron, Leonard Chang, Elmore Leonard (short story "Fire in the Hole")
Actors: Timothy Olyphant, Nick Searcy, Jere Burns, Joelle Carter
Plot: Raylan goes to Memphis to talk to Hot Rod after his men are killed in Mexico, things get tense as Boyd and Darrell wait for the drug shipment, and Boyd and Ava make a deal to get their drugs in prison.
